<p>For this lab, you will explore some of the basics of NLP. As you explore this, you will work with a variety
of methods of the <code>String</code> class and practice using the <code>if</code> statement. You will trace a complicated
method to find words in user input.</p>
<p>Download the <a href="MagpieStudentMaterials.zip" target="_blank">MagpieStudentMaterials.zip</a> file, which contains the Magpie Student Guide and Starter Code for each of the activities. Add the Java files to an Eclipse project. Complete each of the exercises and questions.</p>
